l_main_2528916\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jkp1665702795428.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jkp1665702795428.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jkp1665702795428.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jkp1665702795428\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Resource Browser (Design Layout)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Insert objects from the component structure or code snippets from a selected snippet library into the layout.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jkp1665702795428__section_w3437ab1b7b1_w3438ab1b7_w3439ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jkp1665702795428__section_np3_5k2_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d269433e60\">Tabs</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jkp1665702795428__ul_e3w_5k2_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jkp1665702795428__li_d2636e1_d2637e1_d2638e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Structure</span>—insert objects from\n               the component structure as HTML elements or as binding information into the layout.\n               The object name is added to the id attribute of the corresponding HTML element to\n               bind the HTML to the data. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zur1665702620176.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zur1665702620176.html\" title=\"Binding refers to the way in which layout elements are connected to data structures and triggers in the component structure. It ensures that data is displayed by the appropriate HTML elements in the web page, and that the correct trigger is executed when data in a field is changed.\">Binding Web Layout to Component Structure</a>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jkp1665702795428__li_d2639e1_d2640e1_d2641e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Snippets</span>—insert snippets of\n               HTML code into the layout. Uniface provides a default snippet library called ULAYOUT\n               which contains various HTML fragments for constructing and formatting a layout. For\n               more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"biv1704450635249.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/biv1704450635249.html\" title=\"Snippets are named fragments of code or text that you can insert into your application script or layout to speed development. They are defined as development objects in snippet libraries.\">Snippets</a>. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jkp1665702795428__section_mk4_vk2_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d269433e93\">How to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jkp1665702795428__ul_aqm_wk2_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jkp1665702795428__li_d2642e1_d2643e1_d2644e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hxr1705401640523.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hxr1705401640523.html\" title=\"When creating the layout, elements in the layout must be bound to the component data structure as defined in the Component Editor. You can do this by copying the Uniface objects from the component structure and inserting them as HTML in the layout.\">Insert Uniface Objects in the Server Page Layout</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jkp1665702795428__section_fc5_wk2_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d269433e111\">Shortcut Menu</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jkp1665702795428__table_d527e1_d528e1_d529e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Copy as HTML Menu Commands</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jkp1665702795428__table_d527e1_d528e1_d529e1__entry__1\"> Command </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jkp1665702795428__table_d527e1_d528e1_d529e1__entry__2\"> Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jkp1665702795428__table_d527e1_d528e1_d529e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">As Horizontal\n\t\t\t\t Table</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jkp1665702795428__table_d527e1_d528e1_d529e1__entry__2\">Formats all selected entities and their\n\t\t\t\t content as a horizontal table, with labels in the first row, and entity occurrence data in the\n\t\t\t\t second row. Inner entities are copied as tables within tables.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jkp1665702795428__table_d527e1_d528e1_d529e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">As Unformatted\n\t\t\t\t HTML</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jkp1665702795428__table_d527e1_d528e1_d529e1__entry__2\">Formats the all selected objects as elements\n                     enclosed in <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;div&gt;</code> tags.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jkp1665702795428__table_d527e1_d528e1_d529e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">As Binding\n\t\t\t\t Information</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jkp1665702795428__table_d527e1_d528e1_d529e1__entry__2\">Formats only the object type and name as an\n                        <code class=\"ph codeph\">id</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">name</code> attribute and its value. For\n                     example, <code class=\"ph codeph\">id=\"ufld:BTN_STORE.ORDERS.SALES\"</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528916\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528916\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Resource Browser (Design Layout) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Resource Browser (Design Layout) Insert objects from the component structure or code snippets from a selected snippet library into the layout. Tabs Structure —insert objects from the component structure as HTML elements or as binding information into the layout. The object name is added to the id attribute of the corresponding HTML element to bind the HTML to the data. For more information, see Binding Web Layout to Component Structure . Snippets —insert snippets of HTML code into the layout. Uniface provides a default snippet library called ULAYOUT which contains various HTML fragments for constructing and formatting a layout. For more information, see Snippets . How to Insert Uniface Objects in the Server Page Layout Shortcut Menu Table 1. Copy as HTML Menu Commands Command Description As Horizontal Table Formats all selected entities and their content as a horizontal table, with labels in the first row, and entity occurrence data in the second row. Inner entities are copied as tables within tables. As Unformatted HTML Formats the all selected objects as elements enclosed in <div> tags. As Binding Information Formats only the object type and name as an id or name attribute and its value. For example, id=\"ufld:BTN_STORE.ORDERS.SALES\" Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}